Package com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching

Class GenericContext<T extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.interaction.GenericInteractionCreateEvent>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.dispatching.GenericContext<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ButtonContext, CommandContext
    public class GenericContext<T extends net.dv8tion.jda.api.events.interaction.GenericInteractionCreateEvent>
extends Object
    This class models a command execution. The Parser constructs a new CommandContext for each valid event received. The CommandContext is then passed through the execution chain until it is then transformed into a CommandEvent.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Version:
    2.3.0
    Author:
    Kaktushose
    See Also:
